headline: DATAPAQ TRACKER PLUS
description: Oven Temperature Profiling System    Ideal for belt ovens
specstable:
Manufacturer Datapaq
Model Tracker Plus
Description Oven Temperature Profiling System
Accessories

Four clothes pin clamp thermocouples
One magnetic base thermocouple
Transducer module model T10002C range from 15°C to 265°C
Transducer module model T1-K4-2 range from 30°C to 530°C
Data collection module model MP-F5-5, samples at 5 sec. intervals

Four monitoring channels.
Computer interface RS232 module

Power Requirements 110 V 50/60 Hz 1 Phase
Exterior Dimensions
Width 21.000 in (53.3 cm)
Depth 13.000 in (33.0 cm)
Height 8.000 in (20.3 cm)
Weight 20 lb (9 kg)
